d didhetero: Heterogeneous Treatment Effects in Staggered Difference-in-Differences
d
d Doubly robust uniform confidence bands for group-time conditional
d average treatment effects (CATT) in the staggered difference-in-differences
d framework of Callaway and Sant'Anna (2021), as proposed by
d Imai, Qin, and Yanagi (2025).
d
d Requires: Stata 16.0 or later
d
d Distribution-date: 20260412
d
d Author: Xuanyu Cai, Wenli Xu
d
d Reference:
d   Imai, S., L. Qin, and T. Yanagi. 2025.
d   "Doubly Robust Uniform Confidence Bands for Group-Time Conditional
d   Average Treatment Effects in Difference-in-Differences."
d   Journal of Business & Economic Statistics, 1-13.
d
F ado/didhetero.ado
F ado/didhetero.sthlp
F ado/catt_gt.ado
F ado/catt_gt.sthlp
F ado/aggte_gt.ado
F ado/aggte_gt.sthlp
F ado/catt_gt_graph.ado
F ado/catt_gt_graph.sthlp
F ado/didhetero_simdata.ado
F ado/didhetero_simdata.sthlp
